$ HTML element input (type=button): onclick handler

The following is an attempt to demonstrate how an `onclick` handler can be implemented for a → development/web/HTML/tags/input[`<input type='button' …>`] HTML tag.

gh|about-html|/tags/input/type/button/onclick.html||

